#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:128
msgid ""
"Then, just add this HTML file to the GUI and use the :guilabel:`Convert` "
"button to create your e-book. You can use the option in the Table of "
"Contents section in the conversion dialog to control how the Table of "
